dc_description_s: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Map shows territorial, provincial and district boundaries, 4 classes of roads and railways, towns, rivers, and radioelectrical stations. Aeronautical information is shown. Includes an index to Gazetteer Reference, and a diagram showing magnetic variation 1947. "Administrative Boundaries Revised to May, 1950". "C.B.H. 31181-Wt.3890-Dd.7600-1625-5/58" Original map is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center, map reproduction is attached to companion volume. © Crown copyright 1958.
dc_publisher_s: Dar-es-Salaam : Department of Lands and Surveys, 1950.
